  "architecture_summary": "The paper systematically studies three Vision Transformer families (ViT, DeiT and T2T) and compares them with CNNs, focusing on robustness, shape-vs-texture behavior, positional encoding, and off-the-shelf feature transfer. It also introduces a shape token / shape distillation modification to DeiT and an ensemble-style transfer method using class tokens from multiple blocks.",
